# Java Testing

## Framework

JUnit 5 + wcm.io AEM Mock + Mockito + AssertJ

## Pattern

```java
@ExtendWith({ AemContextExtension.class, MockitoExtension.class })
class MyComponentImplTest {
    private final AemContext context = new AemContext(ResourceResolverType.JCR_MOCK);

    @Mock
    private MyService myService;

    @BeforeEach
    void setUp() {
        context.load().json("/com/example/models/component-content.json", "/content/myproject");
        context.registerService(MyService.class, myService);
        context.addModelsForClasses(MyComponentImpl.class);
    }

    @Test
    void getTitle() {
        context.currentResource("/content/myproject/component1");
        MyComponentImpl model = context.request().adaptTo(MyComponentImpl.class);
        assertEquals("Expected", model.getTitle());
    }
}
```

## Rules

- Always use both `AemContextExtension` and `MockitoExtension`
- Load JCR content from JSON fixture files (in `src/test/resources/`)
- Register all OSGi services the model depends on before adapting
- Use `context.currentResource()` then `context.request().adaptTo()` to test models
- Use AssertJ for assertions, `@ParameterizedTest` + `@CsvSource` for data-driven tests
- Test fixture JSON files live alongside test classes in resources
- Every new Sling Model or service gets a test
- Use BDD-style method names: `shouldDoSomethingWhenCondition()`
- Use AssertJ fluent assertions: `assertThat(result).isEqualTo(expected)`
- Use BDDMockito: `given(...).willReturn(...)` and `then(...).should()`
- Test null safety: verify graceful handling of null inputs and services
- Test JSON export: validate component export structure for headless delivery
- Don't test Core WCM Components — they are tested by Adobe
- Don't test simple getters unless they contain transformation logic
- Don't hardcode test resource paths — use constants or variables
- Skip for simple getter/setter methods or configuration-only classes

## File Organization

```
src/test/
├── java/com/example/project/
│   ├── internal/models/v1/
│   │   └── component/
│   │       └── MyComponentImplTest.java
│   └── services/
│       └── MyServiceImplTest.java
└── resources/com/example/project/
    └── models/
        └── component-content.json
```
